Access palette colors

map_raw_palettes.Rd

Access palette colors

map_raw_palettes(palette)

Arguments

palette

the name of palette

Value

vector of hex colors

Examples

cols <- map_raw_palettes("BYR")
cols
#>  [1] "#000072" "#0D528D" "#277973" "#419973" "#8BB895" "#D7E37D" "#FFFF33"
#>  [8] "#FFB200" "#FF6B01" "#FF3D00" "#FF3D00" "#6E090D" "#000000"
scales::show_col(cols)
